Robert Strauss (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Strauss_(actor) 0 Robert Strauss (November 8, 1913 – February 20, 1975) was an American actor. He became most familiar in Hollywood films of the 1950s such as Stalag 17 (1953), for which he was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor.
